2. DATE PICKER HANDLING
-----------------------

String expectedMonth = "December";
String expectedDate = "26";



IMPORTANT NOTES
---------------

1. Inside While Loop keep ONLY:

   a) Current Year Element
   b) Current Month Element
   c) Next/Previous Button

2. Do NOT use exact locators like:

   //span[text()='December']
   //span[text()='2026']

Reason:
- Month and Year change dynamically.
- Script may fail when calendar opens on another month.

3. Always use generic locators:

   By.className("ui-datepicker-year")
   By.className("ui-datepicker-month")

4. Compare using:

   getText()

5. After month and year match:

   break;

6. Come out of loop and click target date.

